Package cs6310.gui.widget.earth

Interface Summary
TemperatureGrid Implement this interface to allow for the retrieval of information pertaining to a grid of temperatures.
 

Class Summary
EarthGridDisplay Use this class to display an image of the earth with a grid drawn on top.
EarthImage Use this class to get a reference to the JPEG image of the earth.
EarthPanel A JPanel composed of the the earth and sun display components.
SunDisplay This class is a panel displaying the sun as a circle passing over a line representing it's path.
TemperatureColorPicker Use this class to get a color representation of a temperature.
Util Provides utility functions for geometric calculations related to the earth grid.
